{"word":"διάβασις","slug":"διάβασις","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διάβασις</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:διαβαίνω'><el>διαβαίνω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>a crossing over, passage</i>, <el>δ. ποιεῖσθαι</el> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>a means</i> or <i>place of crossing</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>: <el>δ. ποταμοῦ</el> <i>a ford</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>: <i>a bridge</i>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}